@page
@model PrivacyModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About";
}
<h1>About Trace</h1>

<p>
    Trace is a data-management application for gliding competitions: it manages
    competitions, classes, gliders and pilots, sets DHT tasks per class per day,
    and scores flights from uploaded IGC logs. It shares its planning and scoring
    engines with the standalone <code>Trace.Planner</code> and
    <code>Trace.Scorer</code> command-line tools.
</p>
